#     by Damian Conway and Abigail.
#   - Win32::Autoglob
#     http://search.cpan.org/~sburke/Win32-Autoglob-1.01/Autoglob.pm
#     by Sean M. Burke.
#   - Algorithm::Diff
#     http://search.cpan.org/~tyemq/Algorithm-Diff-1.1902/lib/Algorithm/Diff.pm
#     by Tye McQueen.
